Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.74,0:00:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们会在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where could they be?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好几小时之前就该来了的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They should've been here hours ago
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(421.436,374.144)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半个客人都见不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a customer in sight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是今天一分钱都赚不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't make any money today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肯定会起疹子的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll surely break out in a rash
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.46,0:01:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发财了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm rich
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.75,0:01:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八个金币
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eight gold doubloons
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别动  我先看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I saw it first
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.80,0:01:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine, mine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你出的汗真的好多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, Mr. Krabs, you sure are sweaty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.68,0:01:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金币在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are the doubloons?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边没有真金币  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are no real doubloons, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是款桌游
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a game
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼大寻宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Flying Dutchman's Treasure Hunt
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.27,0:01:31.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改编自真正的藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:31.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Based on a real treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(874.087,189)}飞天魔鬼大寻宝
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休息一下  跟咱玩几局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a break and play around with us
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.36,0:01:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来几局吧  流汗的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,C'mon, sweaty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.03,0:01:36.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你擦完桌子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:36.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished cleaning the tables?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擦完桌子了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cleaned the tables, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.62,0:01:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擦完了没错  可底下的口香糖刮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, but did you scrape all the gum off the underside?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.62,0:01:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经办妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already took care of it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, lads
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你们把我拐进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've shanghaied me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.71,0:01:52.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:52.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有一个船友干了坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of your shipmates has been a bad pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关他禁闭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Send him to the brig
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.81,0:02:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要坐牢去了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's off to jail for you, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我都没在这工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't even work here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想不想要现在就开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like a job, starting now?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, would I?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.53,0:02:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,透过古树的树杈寻找执事的鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look for the Deacon's Goose thru the fork in the old tree
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后朝那个方向走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and head that way
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到蟹老板的裤链役拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I see Mr. Krabs' zipper is undone
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.71,0:02:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shiver me timbers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开玩笑而己  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just kidding, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快找到宝藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm almost to the treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮你了蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your turn again, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fish eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.47,0:02:40.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:40.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你变成真正的海盗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are a real pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接前往标有x的藏宝地点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go straight to the "X" which marks the spot
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以挖宝藏了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get to dig for treasure, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Treasure?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是飞天魔鬼的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the Flying Dutchman's Treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金子  金子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gold, gold
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine, mine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板又流好多汗出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is getting all sweaty again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给烤架点火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rev up those fryers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿得好想来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause I am sure hungry for one
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(463.057,428.144)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来我们关门了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see we're closed?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好要再来一局了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for another round?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这游戏跟我很般配
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my kind of game
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:15.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(463.057,428.144)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连赢十七局了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's 17 times in a row
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看我们还是到此为止吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we ought to call it a night, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的得去睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really got to get some sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不能现在就丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't walk out on me now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.11,0:03:34.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁在那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:34.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One more game
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都能闻到宝藏的香气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can smell the treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, it's late
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻风和煦潮正顺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wind is perfect, the tide is right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们快去找宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hunt for treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, you gotta
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脚步放轻点  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tread softly, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是飞天魔鬼听到你声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If the Dutchman hears you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他宝藏就到不了我们手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll never get his treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骰子我帮你掷  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll roll for you, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.46,0:03:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向北八步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,8 paces, north
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开局还真是不错  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a good start, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.05,0:04:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.51,0:04:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想去睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to go to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你知不知道这只是个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's just a game, ya know?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.27,0:04:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A game
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.44,0:04:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实是这样  我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course it is, my mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该是沉迷过头了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I got a little carried away, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然咱在这玩的时光确实珍贵如宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Though it is treasure we're dealing here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰到你了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, for disturbing ya, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.08,0:04:31.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停航
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:31.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Avast
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抵达菠萝屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pineapple, ho
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停下  准备登船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heave to, and prepare to be boarded
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回家行不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go home already
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不玩那个游戏了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm done playing that game, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你讲话的是蟹船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That’s Captain Krabs to you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且这不是游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this is no game
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.01,0:04:49.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要当海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:49.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想要来一场真正的寻宝冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you like to go on a real treasure hunt
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用真正的藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a real treasure map?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Treasure?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要当海盗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要当海盗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Belay that skipping
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗是不跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pirates don't skip
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿上这身海盗服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put on this pirate garb
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我被你们看到才不会觉得尬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I won't be embarrassed to be seen with ya
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, look
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假腿跟眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peg legs and eye patches
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你们是不是更有海盗的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, don't you feel more like pirates?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  我是假腿海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm Peggy the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是瞎胡子海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Blindbeard the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.92,0:05:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,严格戒备  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep a sharp lookout, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根据地图上写的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,According to the map
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们正在接近第一个地标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're close to the first landmark
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能看地图吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we see the map?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有船长才可以看地图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the captain can lay eyes on the map
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okie dokie, then
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗才不会说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pirate doesn't say
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"okie dokie, then"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗要说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pirate says
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.86,0:05:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"arrgh"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.49,0:05:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okie
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  蟹船长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh, Captain Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船长  我们就要触
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain, we're about to hit
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.08,0:05:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:05:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh, Capt.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,arrgh, we're
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  就要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,arrgh, about
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  触
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,arrgh, to hit
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.51,0:06:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有话直说  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out with it man, arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,觉得  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,think, arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's trying, arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to say
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.06,0:06:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,land
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起  只有船长才能说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on, only the captain says, arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,报告状态  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Status report, Mr. SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整艘船都在水底下了  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The whole ship is underwater captain
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被困了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're marooned then
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的接下来的寻宝之旅必须步行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our treasure hunt will have to continue on foot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从双叶海草的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the seaweed with 2 leaves on it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向东10000步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,10,000 paces east
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这海草有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That seaweed has
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向哪走  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which way, cap'n?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星少尉  哪边是东
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ensign Patrick, which way is east?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(673.775,459)}北
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(548.906,641.572)}西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(879.289,554.144)}东
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(767.427,770.144)}南
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That way, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,9997
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9,997
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,9998
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9,998
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,9999
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9,999
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,10000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,0000
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,x哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the "X"?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该就在这的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Supposed to be right here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向东10000步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,10,000 paces east
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向东吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,East?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为你说的是  西东
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you said "weast"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,西东
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weast?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这看的什么指南针  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of compass you reading, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这个  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫向西  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's west, Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606.138,790.715)}西
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,9551
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9,551
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,9552
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9,552
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我们好累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, we're tired
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说我的船员就这水平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So this is my crew
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就累一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get a little tired
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饿一丢丢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a wee bit hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你们就想走人回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you want to shove off for home
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sickens me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.81,0:07:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能靠短剑上的刻痕来评价一个海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pirate is not judged by the notches in his cutlass
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不能靠战利品大小来评价一个海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or by the size of his booty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要靠船员的忠诚度来评价一个海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pirate is judged by the loyalty of his crew
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了忠诚的船员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And without a loyal crew
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当船长指挥什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what am I captain of?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一堆散沙罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a bunch of sand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了  蟹船长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Captain Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我们会当好你的忠诚船员的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll be your loyal crew
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们要跟我留下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll stay with me then?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.75,0:08:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会当好史上最忠诚的海盗船员的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be the most loyal pirate crew ever
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你们靠得住  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew I could count on you boys
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为人人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One for all
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人为我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And all for one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so loyal
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忠诚到都不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even mind
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己睡在又冷又硬的地上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sleeping on the cold, hard ground
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹船长却睡在暖和干燥的帐篷里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while Captain Krabs sleeps in his warm, dry tent
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忠诚到好几周都没洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,, I'm so loyal, I haven't bathed in weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们才刚走几小时而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we've only been gone a few hours
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.98,0:08:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.82,0:08:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忠诚到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so loyal
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找不到宝藏就不睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna sleep till we find the treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们去看下船长要不要出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see if the captain will go now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹船长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The treasure map
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有船长才可以看地图  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the captain can look at the map, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不能看地图的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're not supposed to look at the map
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没看  这是在摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking, I'm touching
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有规定说不可以这样的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no rule against that, is there?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  应该没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, guess there isn't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  它自己展开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, it opened by itself
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The map
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.02,0:09:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The map
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta see it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.02,0:09:10.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得瞧一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:10.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotta look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.36,0:09:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有没有注意到地图有什么熟悉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you notice something familiar about this map?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean, like
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藏宝图是拿咱桌游贴到一张纸上做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that it's our game board taped to a piece of paper?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们觉得这成大问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think this is a problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然偷看我藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sneaking peeks at me treasure map?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我船上发生的叛变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's mutiny on my ship
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你们是不是觉得蟹船长发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you think ol' Captain Krabs has gone crazy, do ye?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全不是的  蟹船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not at all, Captain Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们完全没觉得你疯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't think that at all
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我觉得你疯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你们扔下海作为说错话的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna throw you overboard for saying that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是x
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the "X"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,标x的是藏宝地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"X" marks the spot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:52.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168.05,495)}飞天魔鬼大寻宝
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这游戏还真是改编自真正的藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That game really is based on a real treasure map
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们还等什么  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you waiting for, lads?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dig
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dig
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dig
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挖到了  蟹船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got it, Captain Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它交给我  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand it up to me, lads
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heave
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We finally found it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Dutchman's Treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要用你分到的那份做什么  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do with your share, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要怎么花你分到的那份  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you going to spend your share, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分什么分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What shares?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝藏你们都不准拿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not getting any of my treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我们一起找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We found it together
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们应该要分到一份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we deserve a share
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是船长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm the captain
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说这是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I say it's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么忠诚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about loyalty?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人为我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All for one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为人人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one for all
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.73,0:10:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人为我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All for one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为人人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one for all
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人为我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All for one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为人人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one for all
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁胆敢吵醒飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who dares wake the Flying Dutchman?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep it down will ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to get some sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人为我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All for one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为人人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one for all
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁把飞天魔鬼的宝藏挖出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who dug up the Dutchman's treasure?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They did
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以是你们俩讨厌鬼把我宝藏挖出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you two scallywags dug up me treasure?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们省了我不少挖坑的工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you saved me a lot of diggin' you did
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此这是给你们两个的奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So here's an reward for the two of ya's
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个金币
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two gold doubloons
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是这伙船员的船长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm captain of this crew
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的奖励在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my reward?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看你说得在理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了  一点点小意思给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little something for your trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金子  金子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gold, gold
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是个塑料做的小宝箱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, it's just a little plastic treasure chest
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塑料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plastic
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这可是照着真正的宝箱改编的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's based on a real treasure chest
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又流好多汗出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're looking all sweaty again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.77,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(257,317)}石头滩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(268.572,508)\frz22.54}分镜总监
