Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是在手套乐园度过的欢乐一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another funtastic day at Glove World
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:07.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(261.55,527)}手套乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来拿下钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me get my wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.34,0:12:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找下这个口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let me check this pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  有没有零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, do you have any change?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要多少零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much do you need?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五毛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fifty cents
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五毛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fifty cents
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.43,0:12:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再找下另一个口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me check my other poc-
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.02,0:12:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找位子坐好就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take your seat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  随
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatev-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402.929,421)}手套乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看下你在手套乐园买了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show me what you got at Glove World
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.99,0:12:46.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:46.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的手套灯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's my glove light
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给我的手套手办买了手套
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got gloves for my glove action-figure
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752.335,407)}您正在\N驶出裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.06,0:13:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驶出裤头村是个什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's 'Leaving Bikini Bottom'?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did you see that?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚路过了个路标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just passed the sign
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您已进入驶出裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'You are now in Leaving Bikini Bottom'
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752.335,407)}裤头村界
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我们应该是搭错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I think we're on the wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.37,0:13:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bus
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是司机  我们得回裤头村去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, sir, we need to get back to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.39,0:13:56.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:56.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这啥玩意  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fn@Adobe 黑体 Std R\pos(728.098,630.999)}石头滩
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头滩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(629.133,585)}公较总占
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边真是好诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure is weird around here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kinda different
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连土都看起来不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even the soil looks different
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.16,0:14:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.24,0:14:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mind
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,putting me down?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我不喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I don't like it here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好黑好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's dark and scary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都分不清男女厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't even tell the bathrooms apart
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:28.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(516.032,457)}则所
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很简单的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's an easy one, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等人出来就能分得清男女厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just wait for someone to come out and then you'll know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.89,0:14:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A lady?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或许应该再等一个人出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should wait for one more
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是不懂牌子写的啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still can't read the sign
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来等公交
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wait for the bus
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公交来了叫我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Call me when it comes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去拿公交时刻表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get a bus schedule
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊  这地方真的好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, this place sure is creepy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, the bus is here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.06,0:15:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看海绵爷爷说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess Grandpa SquarePants was right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要追公交车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't run for a bus
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.70,0:15:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别是爬上90度坡的公交车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially one that's going up at a 90-degree angle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好去等下一辆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better go wait for the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:50.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1061.347,445)}公较
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公交快来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,C'mon, bus
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得回家去喂小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to get home and feed Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鞋带松了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shoe's untied
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Under
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再绕上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再绕个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and loop-dee-loop
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再绕上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再穿过口子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and through the barrel
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的气球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快停车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop that bus
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮我个忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you help me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.09,0:16:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的不是气球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.01,0:16:35.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要知道下一班车什么时候来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:35.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to know when the next bus comes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又开走了一辆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there goes another one
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得再好好等下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta be more diligent
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论如何我都不会离开这半步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not leaving this spot no matter what
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.66,0:16:57.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:57.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gettin' hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手套糖果袋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glove candy dispenser
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好我去了手套乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I went to Glove World
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手套味的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glove flavored
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.00,0:17:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那啥东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(742.237,171)}唐果
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糖果售卖机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A candy machine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草牛轧糖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kelp nougat crunch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论如何我都不会离开这半步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving this spot no matter what
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只走开一小会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll only be gone a second
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.13,0:17:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(629.133,315)}海草
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.93,0:18:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was mine
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不当好人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more mister nice guy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死混账
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fish paste
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要搞清这车怎么开的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting to the bottom of this, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:01.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(810.906,593.001)}公较总占
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要一趟回裤头村的车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a bus to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我排第一个  谁都不准瞎扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am first in line and no one is gonna tell me otherwise
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  排第二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, second
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我排第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am second in line
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  第三挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, third is good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第四不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fourth, not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  329
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, 329
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我排第329个  都给我记牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am 329th in line and nobody forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.11,0:19:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少队伍在动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least the line is moving
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.29,0:19:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.09,0:19:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:19:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.26,0:20:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错我就是下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm next
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去裤头村的下一班车什么时候开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When is the next bus to Bikini Bottom?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.06,0:20:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962.382,259)}问讯处
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公交时刻表
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bus schedule
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.27,0:20:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一班车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next bus
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.18,0:20:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,understand
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的口音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your accent
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一班
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next bus
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to Bikini
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:26.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.401,272.999)}问讯处
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你咋不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一班车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next bus leaves in
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五秒后开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,5 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:49.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968.441,286.999)}问讯处
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真倒霉  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tough luck, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那辆是晚上的最后一班车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the last one til' morning
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.33,0:20:33.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:33.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.96,0:20:34.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:34.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.63,0:20:36.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:36.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:59.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(954.305,868.999)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走  我还没说完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it, I'm not through here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I demand you come back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我现在就来一趟到裤头村的车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give me a bus to Bikini Bottom right now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要不来  我就不走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until then, I am not leaving this spot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行吧  就像我说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, like I said
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你回来那会儿  我会在这好好等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right here when you get back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At this spot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一片黑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the dark
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By myself
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With no one around
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好还有手套灯陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except my glove light
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是一般的黑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't your average everyday darkness
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高级黑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,advanced darkness
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是闭上眼睛就不会这么黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I close my eyes, it doesn't seem so dark
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正总站明天也会在那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that spot will be there tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好得一直走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better just keep walking
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.10,0:21:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Running
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好开始跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better start running
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.72,0:21:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Running
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.39,0:21:33.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:33.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Running
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狂奔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sprinting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我最好得狂奔下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I just gotta keep sprinting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sitting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.11,0:21:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sitting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.32,0:21:40.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:40.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bleeding
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.74,0:21:48.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't come closer
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.87,0:21:50.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:50.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.71,0:21:57.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来只是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:57.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.46,0:22:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啦  气球的问题是解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that solves my balloon problem
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还有个更严重的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I have a bigger problem
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有点被困在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda stuck here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要赶公交回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to catch a bus to get home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是听不懂我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't understand a word I'm saying, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.76,0:22:13.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,气球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:13.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.77,0:22:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,enough
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.56,0:22:16.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:16.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,air
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.69,0:22:24.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明白了  坐气球回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:24.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it, balloon travel
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.32,0:22:25.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:25.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.32,0:22:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.74,0:22:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:33.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1107.799,612.999)}正在进入\N石头滩
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可算回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home at last
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.34,0:22:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.68,0:22:50.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming back for ya
